entries.d:
a. Pertaining or allied to, or resembling, asparagus;
having shoots which are eaten like asparagus; as, asparaginous
vegetables.

n. One who asserts or avers; one who maintains or vindicates
a claim or a right; an affirmer, supporter, or vindicator; a defender;
an asserter.

n. Act of assoiling, or state of being assoiled;
absolution; acquittal.
n. A soiling; defilement.
